    java.lang.Runnable, JSParserVisitor

    public class Descripter
extends Visitor<Script<?>>
implements JSParserVisitor

    Represents a visitor to descript parsed JavaScript into Java source.

    Since:
    Descripter 1.0
    Author:
    J.J.Liu (Jianjun Liu) at http://www.descripter.org
